title: 2020 Week 1 Preview
itunes:title: 2020 Week 1 Preview
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler - WE'RE BACK BABY! WE NEVER EVER THOUGHT THIS DAY WOULD COME. WEEK 1. IT'S HAPPENING. STAY CALM! Gregg, as the defending lock champion gets the first overall pick for the game draft (5:10) and takes the Bucs/Saints. Marc, with the second overall pick takes the Cowboys and Rams. (10:51) and Dan takes a surprising first pick that we didn't see coming. (16:23). IT'S SHOWTIME!
